content.text: *Eye to Eye* is a single-screen action platformer that attempts to add to the conversation within the genre, but is also a meditation on personal struggles Austin has gone through in the past year. Processing pain, growth, and redemption through the wonderful creative endeavor that is game design.

content.text: *I Only Have Eye for You* -- Each level starts with the player (who controls the eyeball of a cyclops) jumping out of the cyclops's face to then tackle the challenges of the level. At the end, they make their way back into the eye socket which then smash-cuts into this closeup of the cyclops staring right at the player before transitioning to the next level.

*Austin Serr* is a Los Angeles-based artist whose background is mainly in filmmaking. He is a cinematographer who has shot several feature-length and short films as well as commercials, documentaries, and music videos. He's also had a passion for video games and an interest in game design for years and has decided to finally take the plunge beyond his Super Mario Maker roots to make his first game with *Eye to Eye*.
